4
00:00:01,014 --> 00:00:03,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Follow the traffic rules and drive safely."</b></font>

5
00:00:14,454 --> 00:00:17,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Get ready, yo! Now we blow up the horn</i></b></font>

6
00:00:30,744 --> 00:00:34,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>In the silver smoke amidst the frozen city</i></b></font>

7
00:00:34,474 --> 00:00:38,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Payback for a dream I've seen so many times</i></b></font>

8
00:00:38,144 --> 00:00:41,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My body is frozen in a</i>
<i>memory that I can't shake</i></b></font>

9
00:00:41,814 --> 00:00:45,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Slam on the accelerator and deceive myself</i></b></font>

10
00:00:45,584 --> 00:00:48,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Broken in the night</i></b></font>

11
00:00:48,724 --> 00:00:52,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My eyes become sharper</i></b></font>

12
00:00:52,924 --> 00:00:56,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>All from someone's whim</i></b></font>

13
00:00:56,064 --> 00:01:00,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It seems like the world will end any minute</i></b></font>

14
00:01:00,304 --> 00:01:02,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Break into the night, it's the time</i></b></font>

15
00:01:02,174 --> 00:01:05,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>With scared eyes, I'm lost in the night</i></b></font>

16
00:01:05,844 --> 00:01:09,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Embraced by a falling dream</i></b></font>

17
00:01:09,474 --> 00:01:13,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Scared of being alone, missin' my heart</i></b></font>

18
00:01:13,114 --> 00:01:16,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even hurting myself</i></b></font>

19
00:01:16,924 --> 00:01:20,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Love me so much,</i>
<i>enough that I could fall apart</i></b></font>

20
00:01:20,624 --> 00:01:24,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If only I could throw everything away</i></b></font>

21
00:01:24,264 --> 00:01:27,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And just love you</i></b></font>

22
00:01:27,934 --> 00:01:32,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Then I know I could face the truth</i></b></font>

23
00:02:05,334 --> 00:02:08,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm going at full power,</i>
<i>and he's right on my tail!</i></b></font>

24
00:02:10,034 --> 00:02:13,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No matter how fast I go, I still can't get away!</i></b></font>

25
00:02:15,874 --> 00:02:17,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's no good.</i></b></font>

26
00:02:17,584 --> 00:02:20,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I might lose this race!</i></b></font>

27
00:02:20,514 --> 00:02:22,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ryosuke Takahashi...</i></b></font>

28
00:02:22,884 --> 00:02:26,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't even compare to such a great racer!</i></b></font>

29
00:02:26,424 --> 00:02:29,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm going to lose!</i></b></font>

30
00:02:28,694 --> 00:02:34,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Act 26: The New Downhill Legend!"</b></font>

31
00:03:14,574 --> 00:03:16,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Amazing!</i></b></font>

32
00:03:16,404 --> 00:03:18,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm getting goose bumps.</i></b></font>

33
00:03:18,244 --> 00:03:21,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's following such a perfect line.</i></b></font>

34
00:03:21,244 --> 00:03:25,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If I weren't right behind him,</i>
<i>copying his every move,</i></b></font>

35
00:03:25,744 --> 00:03:31,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>it would have been almost</i>
<i>impossible for me to do this.</i></b></font>

36
00:03:37,724 --> 00:03:40,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Beginners can drive fast on a straight line.</i></b></font>

37
00:03:40,264 --> 00:03:42,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Intermediate drivers can master corners.</i></b></font>

38
00:03:42,394 --> 00:03:45,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But truly advanced drivers</i>
<i>find their own course,</i></b></font>

39
00:03:45,834 --> 00:03:47,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>and that's how they get ahead.</i></b></font>

40
00:03:53,144 --> 00:03:55,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>To find that ultimate course</i></b></font>

41
00:03:55,674 --> 00:03:58,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>is the main objective of</i>
<i>my "fastest driver" theory.</i></b></font>

42
00:03:58,984 --> 00:04:01,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't believe I've found</i>
<i>the best example of my theory</i></b></font>

43
00:04:01,984 --> 00:04:05,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>on such an occasion, after</i>
<i>searching for it for so long.</i></b></font>

44
00:04:08,154 --> 00:04:10,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What amazing talent.</i></b></font>

45
00:04:29,214 --> 00:04:31,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Here they come!
--Which one is it?</b></font>

46
00:04:31,184 --> 00:04:34,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke Takahashi or the Eight-Six?!</b></font>

47
00:04:45,724 --> 00:04:47,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whoa! What intensity!</b></font>

48
00:04:47,734 --> 00:04:50,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How impressive!</b></font>

49
00:04:58,004 --> 00:05:00,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's no good! I can't widen the lead!</i></b></font>

50
00:05:05,214 --> 00:05:07,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right! They're coming!</b></font>

51
00:05:07,314 --> 00:05:10,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just the sound of it gives me shivers!</b></font>

52
00:05:10,484 --> 00:05:15,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since the straight section before
the five hairpins is quite long,</b></font>

53
00:05:15,054 --> 00:05:18,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I bet there'll be some hard braking.</b></font>

54
00:05:22,164 --> 00:05:25,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here they come! The Eight-Six is in front!</b></font>

55
00:05:25,104 --> 00:05:26,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ryosuke!</i></b></font>

56
00:05:30,004 --> 00:05:32,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Entrance to the five hairpins here.</b></font>

57
00:05:32,344 --> 00:05:35,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can see both cars now.
The Eight-Six is leading!</b></font>

58
00:05:35,744 --> 00:05:38,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow, the Eight-Six?!</b></font>

59
00:05:51,724 --> 00:05:54,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Too much speed. He messed it up.</i></b></font>

60
00:05:58,534 --> 00:06:00,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Damn it! Turn!</i></b></font>

61
00:06:10,314 --> 00:06:12,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He could have powered through it</i></b></font>

62
00:06:12,314 --> 00:06:16,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>and brought it back if he were</i>
<i>driving a more powerful car.</i></b></font>

63
00:06:16,554 --> 00:06:18,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But how reckless to try it with an Eight-Six!</i></b></font>

64
00:06:19,924 --> 00:06:22,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke's FC took the lead!</b></font>

65
00:06:22,824 --> 00:06:24,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

66
00:06:24,664 --> 00:06:27,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When the Eight-Six over-accelerated</b></font>

67
00:06:27,264 --> 00:06:32,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and under-steered, Ryosuke passed it!</b></font>

68
00:06:32,264 --> 00:06:34,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The Eight-Six under-steered?</i></b></font>

69
00:06:36,934 --> 00:06:41,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's just amazing!
Ryosuke is in a class by himself!</b></font>

70
00:06:41,274 --> 00:06:44,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now I am totally sure that
Ryosuke is going to win!</b></font>

71
00:07:00,834 --> 00:07:02,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Such a strange guy...</i></b></font>

72
00:07:02,334 --> 00:07:04,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What an unexpected weakness!</i></b></font>

73
00:07:04,864 --> 00:07:06,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I was planning to stay</i>
<i>behind him a little longer</i></b></font>

74
00:07:06,934 --> 00:07:09,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>so I could hide my strengths.</i></b></font>

75
00:07:09,104 --> 00:07:12,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Now that I'm in front, I don't</i>
<i>want him to get right behind me,</i></b></font>

76
00:07:12,544 --> 00:07:16,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>so before he recovers, I'd better widen the gap</i></b></font>

77
00:07:16,044 --> 00:07:18,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>and guarantee myself the win.</i></b></font>

78
00:07:38,304 --> 00:07:40,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The FC just passed us.</b></font>

79
00:07:40,404 --> 00:07:42,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six is a little behind.</b></font>

80
00:07:42,634 --> 00:07:44,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke's time is amazing!</b></font>

81
00:07:44,904 --> 00:07:48,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He could beat the course record
by almost twelve seconds!</b></font>

82
00:07:48,844 --> 00:07:51,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Twelve seconds?!</i></b></font>

83
00:07:51,544 --> 00:07:53,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The race is over.</i></b></font>

84
00:07:53,854 --> 00:07:56,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My brother will just widen the gap now.</i></b></font>

85
00:08:00,024 --> 00:08:04,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just hearing about it gives me chills.</b></font>

86
00:08:04,194 --> 00:08:07,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even if he loses, it won't
hurt Takumi's reputation.</b></font>

87
00:08:07,394 --> 00:08:10,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's just that Ryosuke Takahashi
is simply incomparable!</b></font>

88
00:08:10,264 --> 00:08:12,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wait a minute. The race isn't over yet!</b></font>

89
00:08:12,934 --> 00:08:16,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I still believe that Takumi
can come back and win.</b></font>

90
00:08:16,504 --> 00:08:18,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But...</b></font>

91
00:08:18,104 --> 00:08:20,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He always has, hasn't he?!</b></font>

92
00:08:20,774 --> 00:08:24,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No matter how bad it's looked,
he's always come back and won.</b></font>

93
00:08:24,614 --> 00:08:28,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I am sure he can do it again!</b></font>

94
00:08:34,194 --> 00:08:38,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Please get to the bottom safely!</i></b></font>

95
00:08:38,024 --> 00:08:41,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't do anything crazy, Takumi!</i></b></font>

96
00:08:57,784 --> 00:09:03,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The merit of a light and compact</i>
<i>rotary engine is not the power,</i></b></font>

97
00:09:03,154 --> 00:09:08,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but the agility you get from an</i>
<i>ideal front-back weight distribution.</i></b></font>

98
00:09:08,724 --> 00:09:16,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I just love the consistent</i>
<i>spirit of the rotary engine.</i></b></font>

99
00:09:16,394 --> 00:09:17,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even if I have to put my pride on the line,</i></b></font>

100
00:09:17,904 --> 00:09:21,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>the rotary engine can't fall behind</i>
<i>the Eight-Six on the corners!</i></b></font>

101
00:09:37,984 --> 00:09:40,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whoa!</b></font>

102
00:09:44,994 --> 00:09:48,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Aren't Ryosuke Takahashi and Takumi great?</b></font>

103
00:09:48,534 --> 00:09:52,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The drift punks around here don't
even come close to that speed.</b></font>

104
00:09:52,504 --> 00:09:56,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sayuki, what's going to happen in this race?</b></font>

105
00:09:56,374 --> 00:10:01,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's impossible to pass
Ryosuke once he's in front.</b></font>

106
00:10:01,374 --> 00:10:05,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But it's Takumi he's racing against!</b></font>

107
00:10:05,484 --> 00:10:08,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi hasn't given up yet.</b></font>

108
00:10:08,314 --> 00:10:11,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The lines he chooses are better than the FC's.</b></font>

109
00:10:11,684 --> 00:10:14,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can tell he's driven Akina Pass a lot.</b></font>

110
00:10:27,574 --> 00:10:33,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I thought he would be way</i>
<i>ahead once he passed me!</i></b></font>

111
00:10:33,344 --> 00:10:35,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I still have a chance!</i></b></font>

112
00:10:42,884 --> 00:10:45,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm getting closer!</i></b></font>

113
00:10:45,754 --> 00:10:48,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The gap is narrowing!</i></b></font>

114
00:10:52,824 --> 00:10:54,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Shoot!</i></b></font>

115
00:10:54,164 --> 00:10:58,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>All of a sudden, my front tires</i>
<i>aren't sticking to the road.</i></b></font>

116
00:10:58,664 --> 00:11:00,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Could it be heat wear?</i></b></font>

117
00:11:04,674 --> 00:11:07,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Following and copying the Eight-Six's driving</i></b></font>

118
00:11:07,344 --> 00:11:10,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>might have put more strain on</i>
<i>the front tires than I expected.</i></b></font>

119
00:11:16,354 --> 00:11:18,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The Eight-Six is getting closer...</i></b></font>

120
00:11:18,884 --> 00:11:21,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Isn't he having any problems with his tires?</i></b></font>

121
00:11:26,024 --> 00:11:31,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A little wear on the tires won't</i>
<i>affect my technique, though.</i></b></font>

122
00:11:51,824 --> 00:11:55,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't catch him like this.</i>
<i>I need to get closer all at once!</i></b></font>

123
00:12:08,174 --> 00:12:10,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Darn it! Is this my limit?</i></b></font>

124
00:12:11,644 --> 00:12:13,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Should I try that thing?</i></b></font>

125
00:12:13,344 --> 00:12:17,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The "other gutter driving" that</i>
<i>my dad talked about that time?</i></b></font>

126
00:12:28,354 --> 00:12:30,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, good job.</b></font>

127
00:12:32,464 --> 00:12:35,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Dad. I think I found a good trick</b></font>

128
00:12:35,434 --> 00:12:38,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to avoid skidding on a
curve in snowy weather.</b></font>

129
00:12:40,304 --> 00:12:43,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You hook the tires on one side
into the gutter next to the road.</b></font>

130
00:12:43,334 --> 00:12:46,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can corner so easily, it's like a joke.</b></font>

131
00:12:48,674 --> 00:12:50,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Gutter driving," huh?</b></font>

132
00:12:50,474 --> 00:12:53,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I use that technique often, too.</b></font>

133
00:12:53,184 --> 00:12:55,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shoot. You use it too, huh?</b></font>

134
00:12:55,454 --> 00:12:59,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi. There are two ways to
use the gutters in Akina's roads.</b></font>

135
00:12:59,684 --> 00:13:02,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The method you discovered is to
use the gutter as you enter the corner</b></font>

136
00:13:02,994 --> 00:13:06,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so you can prevent under-steering.</b></font>

137
00:13:07,394 --> 00:13:11,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's another one. This one
emphasizes recovery after a corner.</b></font>

138
00:13:11,804 --> 00:13:15,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The timing for getting both in
and out of the gutter is different.</b></font>

139
00:13:15,404 --> 00:13:19,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's pretty tough. Try and
figure it out for yourself.</b></font>

140
00:13:23,574 --> 00:13:25,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I haven't tried it yet.</i></b></font>

141
00:13:25,984 --> 00:13:28,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's a big gamble. Should I try it?</i></b></font>

142
00:13:32,024 --> 00:13:35,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Okay. Here I go!</i></b></font>

143
00:13:52,744 --> 00:13:55,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What did he just do?!</b></font>

144
00:14:07,224 --> 00:14:10,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What the heck did he just do?!</i></b></font>

